{"id": 59733, "date": "2025-09-28T04:00:33", "date_gmt": "2025-09-28T11:00:33", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59733"}, "modified": "2026-06-01T20:13:15", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-02T03:13:15", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-28-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/28/kingdom-of-days-september-28-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 28"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>Bruce headlines at the Off Broad Street Coffee House in Red Bank, performing two acoustic solo set.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4556\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1968-0928/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0928.jpg?fit=800%2C474&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"800,474\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1968-0928\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0928.jpg?fit=758%2C449&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4556 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0928.jpg?resize=758%2C449&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0928.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0928.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0928.jpg?resize=768%2C455&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>The Wild &amp; Innocent Tour kicks off at Virginia&#8217;s Hampden-Sydney College, where &#8220;The E Street Shuffle&#8221; makes its debut, featuring the band&#8217;s first-ever guest artist: Albee Tellone on baritone sax.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4557\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-0928/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1973-0928.jpg?fit=700%2C632&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"700,632\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-0928\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1973-0928.jpg?fit=700%2C632&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4557 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1973-0928.jpg?resize=700%2C632&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"632\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1973-0928.jpg?w=700&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1973-0928.jpg?resize=300%2C271&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974: </strong>Bruce&#8217;s scheduled show at Drew University in Madison, New Jersey (this blogger&#8217;s alma mater), is canceled less than 48 hours before showtime&#8211;because Bruce was booked at five other colleges for that same date. Rather than breach four contracts by choosing one, Bruce cancels on all five.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21464\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-09-28a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28a.jpg?fit=713%2C927&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"713,927\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600621812&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-09-28a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28a.jpg?fit=713%2C927&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21464 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28a.jpg?resize=713%2C927&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"713\" height=\"927\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28a.jpg?w=713&amp;ssl=1 713w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28a.jpg?resize=231%2C300&amp;ssl=1 231w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 713px) 100vw, 713px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29701\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-09-28b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1974-09-28b.jpg?fit=506%2C870&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"506,870\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600621896&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-09-28b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1974-09-28b.jpg?fit=506%2C870&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29701 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1974-09-28b.jpg?resize=506%2C870&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"870\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1974-09-28b.jpg?w=506&amp;ssl=1 506w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1974-09-28b.jpg?resize=174%2C300&amp;ssl=1 174w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21466\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-09-28c/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28c.jpg?fit=258%2C449&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"258,449\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600621957&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-09-28c\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28c.jpg?fit=258%2C449&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21466 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28c.jpg?resize=258%2C449&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"258\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28c.jpg?w=258&amp;ssl=1 258w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1974-09-28c.jpg?resize=172%2C300&amp;ssl=1 172w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays in Kansas for the first time when the Born to Run Tour stops at Memorial Hall in Kansas City.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JcRLB5zG-dI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4559\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0928/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?fit=1268%2C444&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1268,444\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0928\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?fit=758%2C266&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4559 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?resize=758%2C265&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"265\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?w=1268&amp;ssl=1 1268w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?resize=300%2C105&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?resize=768%2C269&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0928-e1780369961290.jpg?resize=1024%2C359&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session at The Record Plant in New York City, where he and the band work on &#8220;The Promise.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ksRM63yzF2c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>On\u00a0<em>American Top 40,\u00a0</em>host Casey Kasem shares an anecdote from one of Bruce&#8217;s Castiles bandmates.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-59733-4\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/AT40-1985-09-28.mp3?_=4\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/AT40-1985-09-28.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/AT40-1985-09-28.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1986:\u00a0</strong>Bruce attends\u00a0<em>Lady Beth</em>, a play by laid-off Freehold 3M plant workers at The Stone Pony, where he gives a short speech of support and encouragement.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QHUFaCmnesU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21470\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1986-09-28a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?fit=1403%2C1644&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1403,1644\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600622303&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1986-09-28a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?fit=758%2C888&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21470 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?resize=758%2C888&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"888\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?w=1403&amp;ssl=1 1403w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?resize=256%2C300&amp;ssl=1 256w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?resize=874%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 874w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?resize=768%2C900&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-28a.jpg?resize=1311%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1311w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>At the final night (of three) in Los Angeles on World Tour 1992, Danny Federici joins Bruce&#8217;s new touring band for the encore set.</p>\n<div id=\"v-dKW1FRfa-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/dKW1FRfa?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Night Two in Chicago on the Reunion Tour brings a &#8220;Don&#8217;t Look Back&#8221; opener and the last &#8220;Something in the Night&#8221; for the year.</p>\n<div id=\"v-2kOwyH8b-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/2kOwyH8b?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-IYSv4MYl-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/IYSv4MYl?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XuIG0fOjsys?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2004:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse at Asbury Park&#8217;s Convention Hall for their upcoming Vote for Change Tour.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21471\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2004-09-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?fit=867%2C1636&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"867,1636\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600623086&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2004-09-28\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?fit=543%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21471 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?resize=758%2C1430&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1430\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?w=867&amp;ssl=1 867w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?resize=159%2C300&amp;ssl=1 159w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?resize=543%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 543w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?resize=768%2C1449&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2004-09-28.jpg?resize=814%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 814w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Promoting their new\u00a0<em>Magic\u00a0</em>album and upcoming tour, Bruce and the E Street Band perform a live morning concert on NBC&#8217;s <em>Today</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Hs8ihdlkNsc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21472\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2007-09-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?fit=1620%2C1640&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1620,1640\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600623375&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2007-09-28\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?fit=758%2C767&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21472 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?resize=758%2C767&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"767\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?w=1620&amp;ssl=1 1620w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?resize=296%2C300&amp;ssl=1 296w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?resize=1012%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1012w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?resize=768%2C777&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?resize=1517%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1517w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-09-28.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p>That evening, Bruce and the band play a benefit rehearsal show, where they debut a new rock arrangement for &#8220;Reason to Believe.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/00XApeB2Wgg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-OA2sHml1-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/OA2sHml1?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iVxCjIki7tU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016: </strong>In New York City, Bruce makes a promotional appearance at Barnes &amp; Noble in Union Square in support of his newly published autobiography. Later, at the Soho Apple Store in New York City, Bruce is interviewed by Apple&#8217;s Eddy Cue<em>.</em> The event is simulcast on Facebook Live.</p>\n<div id=\"v-2IPVWGxy-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/2IPVWGxy?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong>To help offset high ticket prices,\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> announces a daily lottery for a limited number of inexpensive tickets to the show.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HWYbyDskN74?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. Patti is absent again tonight, so Bruce adds an extra encore of &#8220;This Hard Land&#8221; in place of his duet of &#8220;Tougher Than the Rest&#8221; with Patti.</p>\n<p><strong>2019:\u00a0</strong>Bruce spends the day at his daughter&#8217;s equestrian competition in New York. That evening, he stops by his hometown of Freehold to visit the opening of the Monmouth County Historical Association Museum&#8217;s new exhibit,\u00a0<em>Springsteen: His Home Town.</em>\u00a0 After touring the exhibit, Bruce surprises the assembled crowd by taking the stage with Joe Grushecky and The Houserockers for their opening number, &#8220;Light of Day.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mR8LH8Hxsgs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"News 12 NJ TV - \u201cSpringsteen: His Hometown\u201d (abbreviated segment) - 9/27/19\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/362791995?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\"></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hMD9P2soxIY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21475\" data-permalink=